{"tid":2458685,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"土耳其股市連續兩日觸發二級熔斷　跌幅高達7%","createTime":"2021-03-23T15:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T17:52:30.000Z","uid":295230,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9db3e7c86114f541a26454788909d1580b297106","tid":2458685,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"土耳其總統埃爾多安上周末突然宣布罷免該國央行行長阿巴爾（Naci Agbal），並任命支持「鴿派」的卡夫哲奥盧（Sahap Kavcioglu）出任新行長。市場憂慮土耳其會轉向減息，該國貨幣土耳其里拉一度暴瀉，連同該國股市亦受牽連。<br />\n<br />\n今日亞洲時間下午，土耳其基準股指開市跌5.4%，已觸發熔斷。其後跌幅擴大至7%，連續兩日觸發二級熔斷。當地的伊斯坦布爾證券交易所一度宣布，股票市場、衍生品市場的股票和股票指數合約以及債務證券股票回購市場的交易暫停。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，土耳其總統經濟顧問布盧特再次強調要保持低利率，認為該國將專注於經濟增長和低利率，利率應該處於經濟現實允許的範圍內。但他又指，土耳其央行不會採取任何特別行動。"},{"pid":"d6d2569d2c22e5935004575a7aefd10de8fa2a8a","tid":2458685,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"慘"},{"pid":"31bf93973e8baadcaa4a0b9f90eef7b96d6476ca","tid":2458685,"uid":306861,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a43fe724bc2ac1c3c235085432ad7d911dd8023","tid":2458685,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"上面2個bot<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a713424d5836538434babccfa2d0e5cc573bd85b","tid":2458685,"uid":379298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"教主"},{"pid":"12f74790e5a18c1031c9acd6aea380dd5592f668","tid":2458685,"uid":8113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6d2569d2c22e5935004575a7aefd10de8fa2a8a","tid":2458685,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:19:26.000Z","msg":"慘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"